snippet.title: Got the Time || E01 || Later Alligator Adventure [Let's Play]
snippet.description:
We got ourselves an excellent fitting pinstripe suit and found ourselves in a fancy alligator new york restaurant chatting with a rather nervous fellow called Pat. Apparently there is an Event later that he would like us to investigate.

I figure why not. These alligators seem friendly enough let's have ourselves some minigames.
